<div class='comment type_comment' ><a name="1436793247">&nbsp;</a><strong>[2015-07-13 13:14 UTC] <a href="//people.php.net/cmb">cmb@php.net</a></strong>
<pre class='note'>Description:
------------
Apparently, imagescale(..., IMG_BICUBIC) leaks memory.


Test script:
---------------
&lt;?php
$im = imagecreatetruecolor(256, 256);
imagescale($im, 32, 32, IMG_BICUBIC);
imagedestroy($im);
?&gt;


